Wait for it!!! 😍 The makings of a fluffy omelette cannot be missed! 😍🙌🏼❤️
Follow @hungryhugh for more food! 🙌🏼 Checkout my Snapchat 👻: HungryHugh!
🍳
🍴: Omurice
👉🏼: @kichikichi_kyoto
📍: Kichikichi,中京区材木町185-4
Kyoto, 京都府 〒604-8017 Japan
🍚
@kichikichi_kyoto’s OMURICE (open omelette over fried rice) is one of the best dishes I’ve had here in Kyoto! The omelette is fluffy, the fried rice has tons of flavor and that special sauce will make your eyes roll back! 😂👌🏼😍 Thank you @hulagirl7 for all your help! 😘❤️

Piña Nada or a Seaside drink?! 🔥🙌🏼💙 The Piña Nada is what I need rn! 🤗🍍
✌🏼
‼️ Support your local restaurants by ordering food for pick-up or delivery! You’ll help the restaurant and their staff during this unprecedented time. Please stay healthy and safe! 🙏🏼❤️
Follow @hungryhugh for more food! 🙌🏼
🍍
🍴: Piña Nada & Seaside
👉🏼: @bobabreakteahouse
📍: Boba Break Tea House at the Glendora Public Market, 905 E Arrow Hwy, Glendora, CA 91740
🌊
@bobabreakteahouse’s PIÑA NADA & SEASIDE will keep you cool with all this heat! 🥵👌🏼 The Piña Nada is pineapple slush with chamoy and tajin! 🔥 The Seaside has brown sugar whole milk with pea tea and topped with sea salt cream. 🤓🙌🏼
.
